# Reuse First, Then Extend

Before creating new services/utilities, check and reuse these interfaces first:
- Bridge API: `plugins/live_photo_bridge/lib/live_photo_bridge.dart` (`LivePhotoBridge`)
- Media service: `lib/services/live_photo_manager.dart` (`LivePhotoManager`)
- Layout engine: `lib/services/layout_engine.dart` (`LayoutEngine.calculateLayout`)
- Unified block model: `lib/models/image_block.dart` (`ImageBlock`)

Mandatory:
- If a new feature overlaps with an existing interface, extend the existing one first.
- If you still add a new interface, include a short code comment explaining why reuse is not possible.
- Keep business logic out of screens if it can live in `services`.

Avoid:
- Duplicating bridge calls in multiple places.
- Re-implementing layout algorithms inside UI files.
- Introducing alternate block models with the same semantics as `ImageBlock`.
